# API Contracts: MyUS University Portal System

## Authentication

- `POST /api/auth/login`
  - request: `{ username, password }`
  - response: `{ accessToken, tokenType, expiresIn, user: { id, role } }`

- `POST /api/auth/logout`
  - request: auth token
  - response: `{ message }`

## Student Profile

- `GET /api/students/me`
  - response: student profile data

- `PUT /api/students/me`
  - request: profile update fields
  - response: updated profile

## Grade Appeal

- `POST /api/appeals`
  - request: `{ gradeId, reason, supportingDocumentUrl }`
  - response: created appeal

- `GET /api/appeals/me`
  - response: list of student appeals

- `GET /api/appeals/{appealId}`
  - response: appeal details and status

- `PUT /api/appeals/{appealId}/process`
  - request: `{ status, reviewerComments }`
  - response: updated appeal

## Course Enrollment

- `GET /api/courses`
  - response: available courses and offerings

- `POST /api/registrations`
  - request: `{ offeringId }`
  - response: registration confirmation

- `GET /api/registrations/me`
  - response: student timetable and enrollment records

## GPA & Academic Records

- `GET /api/grades/me`
  - response: grade summary and GPA

- `GET /api/academic-records/me`
  - response: transcript and cumulative records

## Timetable

- `GET /api/timetable/me`
  - response: class schedule and exam schedule

## Tuition Tracking

- `GET /api/tuition/me`
  - response: balance, payments, scholarship details

## Survey System

- `GET /api/surveys`
  - response: available surveys

- `POST /api/surveys/{surveyId}/responses`
  - request: survey answers
  - response: submission confirmation

## FAQ System

- `GET /api/faqs`
  - response: FAQ articles and search results

## Student Administration

- `GET /api/admin/students`
  - request: optional search filters
  - response: list of student records

- `POST /api/admin/import`
  - request: bulk import file payload
  - response: import job status and validation details

## Class Management

- `GET /api/admin/transfers`
  - response: class transfer requests

- `POST /api/admin/transfers/{transferId}`
  - request: `{ status, reviewerComments }`
  - response: updated transfer request

## AI Learning Path Chatbot

- `POST /api/chatbot/recommendations`
  - request: `{ studentId, context }`
  - response: recommended courses and progress guidance

## Security Contract Notes

- All protected endpoints require `Authorization: Bearer <token>`.
- Role-based access is enforced on `/api/admin/*` and student-specific resources.
- API responses must omit sensitive financial or academic details for unauthorized users.
